data.description: This home is waiting for you to come sit and rock away on the front porch. Open floor plan with vaulted ceiling making the home very spacious. Plantation shutters in the great room and dining area. Kitchen, dining room & baths have tile flooring and LVP throughout the rest of the home. NO CARPET. Dining room has pretty light fixture and all open to the kitchen  Stainless stove, microwave & dishwasher in the kitchen .with breakfast bar & white cabinets. Laundry room is located in the hall way. Master bedroom has a nice master bath. 2 guest rooms share the hall bath. Vinyl fencing and  brick paver walk way leading to a large patio area, perfect for grilling out. Single garage. This home is centrally located and close to everything.
